#include<iostream>
#include<fstream>
#include<cstdio>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;

int main(){
    //freopen("input_knp2.txt","r",stdin);
    int t;
    cin>>t;
    int c_t=0;
    while(t--){
        c_t++;
        cout<<"Case "<<c_t<<":"<<endl;
        int n,q, i, j;
        cin>>n>>q;
        int a[n+1];
        int te;
        string s;
        for(i=0; i<n; i++){
            cin>>s;
            a[i] = 0;
            if(s[0] == '0'){
                for(j=2; j<s.length(); j++){
                    //te = 10;
                    a[i] = a[i] *10+(s[j]-'0');
                }
            }
            else{
                for(j=0; j<s.length(); j++){
                    a[i] = a[i] *10+(s[j]-'0');
                }
                a[i] *= 100;
            }
        }
        sort(a, a+n);
        int x;
        int c_q=0;
        while(q--){
            c_q++;
            cout<<"Scenario "<<c_q<<":"<<endl;
            cin>>s;
            int flag_dot = 0;
            te = 1;
            x=0;
            for(j=0; j<s.length(); j++){
                if(s[j]=='.'){
                    flag_dot = 1;
                    continue;
                }
                x = x *10+(s[j]-'0');
            }
            if(flag_dot == 0){
                x *= 100;
            }
            for(i=n-1; i>=0; i--){
                if(a[i]==0)
                    continue;
                if(x/a[i]){
                    if(a[i]>=100)
                        cout<<a[i]/100<<" "<<(x/a[i])<<endl;
                    else if(a[i]>=10){
                        printf("0.%d %d\n",a[i],x/a[i]);
                    }
                    else
                        printf("0.0%d %d\n",a[i],x/a[i]);
                    x%=a[i];
                }
            }
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
